WEBVTT

00:08:29.828 --> 00:08:31.951
Let there be waves of positivity,

00:08:31.975 --> 00:08:33.493
thundering applause,

00:08:33.517 --> 00:08:36.565
villages full of women
who bleed with pride.

00:08:36.953 --> 00:08:39.203
Let there be a scent of education

00:08:39.227 --> 00:08:44.093
drifting through the oxygen
inhaled by men, women and children.

00:08:44.117 --> 00:08:47.328
Let all know the marvels of menstruation

00:08:47.352 --> 00:08:49.594
and celebrate Pravahkriti."

00:08:50.194 --> 00:08:51.349
Thank you.

00:08:51.373 --> 00:08:54.484
(Applause)